  "texts": [
    "You may look at the heights of buildings that are listed in prior permits over time, keep track of how limits in the legislation have changed, and release a survey about preferences for people who live in the neighborhood.",
    "So far, this scenario might seem pretty straightforward and low risk for ethical complications.",
    "However, let's dig in a bit more.",
    "What about the people who cannot afford to live in the neighborhood but commute there for work?",
    "The commute may take up considerable free time and so they like to take advantage of the green space nearby their office building to eat their lunch and get some fresh air."
  ]
}